"Internal Use" means use solely for the benefit of the user or Organization itself and not for providing services or functionality to unrelated third parties.

"Hosted Service" means providing the functionality of the Software, directly or indirectly, to one or more third parties through a network, including but not limited to SaaS, PaaS, managed services, cloud services, APIs, web services, or similar offerings.

"Single-Customer Managed Deployment" means operation of the Software exclusively for one identified customer in a dedicated environment that is not shared with other customers.

"Commercial Product" means any software product, appliance, platform, service, or solution offered to third parties for commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

"Distribution" means making the Software or a Derivative Work available to any third party in source code form, binary form, container form, appliance form, or any other form.

